---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout>
  <div class="mission-container">
    <h1>Our Mission</h1>
    <p>Our website is a smart learning platform designed to help students prepare better with clarity and confidence. We provide high-quality study content, exam-oriented blogs, current affairs, mock tests, previous year questions, and digital tools to track daily syllabus progress.</p>
    <p>Our goal is to make learning simple, structured, and accessible for every student. All content is regularly updated, easy to understand, and focused on real exam needs. With a clean design and user-friendly experience, students can study, revise, and improve without any technical hassle.</p>
    <p>If you're looking for a reliable and modern study companion, our platform is built for you.</p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .mission-container {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 2rem;
    text-align: center;
  }
  h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  p {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
</style>
